{"tid":415523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反港獨、辱華、資本主義、兩制 大聯盟","createTime":"2017-09-27T04:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T05:03:18.000Z","uid":63841,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c97fd03cfb433fff1f8e00c88e319cb3df444540","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"作為住喺香港嘅中國人，我哋應該要搞返個 反港獨 反辱華 反資本主義 反兩制 大聯盟 <br />\n<br />\n呢個&quot;反獨聯&quot; 主張四反對<br />\n<br />\n1） 反港獨: 港獨 影響社會安寧，分裂國家，係政客換取政治本錢嘅偽命題 。<br />\n<br />\n2）反辱華: 由梁游事件可見有一部分嘅香港人嘗試否認自己中國人嘅身份， 甚至出言侮辱全球華人，侮辱中華民族。<br />\n<br />\n3）反資本主義: 資本主義導致 貧者越貧，富者越富。現今中國香港嘅青年 因為失去向上流動的機會而被西方大國煽動去仇視中國，支持港獨等不切實際之主張， 所以我哋要反對西方邪惡嘅資本主義，擁抱國家一直提倡嘅共產思想，令到人人平等。<br />\n<br />\n4）反兩制: 港澳特區同胞藉住我哋中國給予嘅兩制而嘗試去區分兩地人民身分，否定其中國人之身份，所以我哋要反對兩制，回歸一國"},{"pid":"95b8d0872e9863f5494b6c56489acd310dbea53b","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:55:14.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀: 真愛聯"},{"pid":"44b76058a6b9ffe8ef8e0e1105109756ceb14a9e","tid":415523,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"支持一國一制 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970ac613e43df4128804bcba3fd925ee90f8cd15","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"再延伸閱讀<br />\n貼劉曉波係近年最精彩既政治操作<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/396203/page/1?ref=web\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/396203/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57705ed9ae4521a13f20d513bca7f5ef3e3bc667","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:59:10.000Z","msg":"睇到香港嘅年輕人對我哋中國存有咁深嘅誤解，又被煽動去仇中，撐港獨，我好心痛"},{"pid":"465f6fc3a1115985583a48d491b29cb380daea89","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"大家從民主牆都睇到香港大學生幾咁胡作非為，為咗威，就咗得到朋輩認同而宣揚錯誤嘅主張，港獨真係會搞死香港㗎"},{"pid":"faf24106dd09a642211e11fced84cefbeb73714c","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:00:33.000Z","msg":"依家班香港後生仔搞示威搞抗爭搞得咁開心， 我哋應該係香港搞返場文化大革命宣揚毛思想。反對好似戴耀廷咁嘅知識分子反中亂港"},{"pid":"55e5d3893794b5dc4cb1f6d200833ce6e4d56b7d","tid":415523,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:01:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>學下貼圖啦</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140419/large/1397909704_7998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140419%2Flarge%2F1397909704_7998.jpg&h=d247a553&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4754e457e20d2cad1fd6c27e0b36d5f5496cfa68","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/130258_fd7d64af26d5edbe4e04eddb43e723fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F130258_fd7d64af26d5edbe4e04eddb43e723fa.jpg&h=3df1f1ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"227cd0665697ef3a2594d5e634e09d2d8a30363d","tid":415523,"uid":63841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T05:03:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>學下貼圖啦</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140419/large/1397909704_7998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140419%2Flarge%2F1397909704_7998.jpg&h=d247a553&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}